-{"id":"bd-33eoe","title":"[Bug] WebSocketHub handleReconnect can double-send ack-required messages","description":"In `apps/gateway/src/ws/hub.ts`, `handleReconnect()` replays missed messages for a channel and adds them to `pendingAcks`, then calls `replayPendingAcks()` which re-sends those newly-added pending messages a second time.\n\nThis can cause duplicate delivery on reconnect for ack-required channels.\n\nFix: ensure `replayPendingAcks()` only replays acks that existed prior to reconnect (or otherwise de-dupe against messages already replayed in this reconnect pass). Add regression test in `apps/gateway/src/ws/__tests__/ack-mode.test.ts`.","notes":"Blocked: NavyFinch currently holds exclusive reservations on hub.ts and ack-mode test; waiting for handoff or upstream fix.","status":"blocked","priority":2,"issue_type":"bug","assignee":"MagentaCompass","created_at":"2026-01-31T00:31:22.968156231Z","created_by":"MagentaCompass","updated_at":"2026-01-31T00:32:23.915797109Z","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-33eoe","depends_on_id":"bd-1ns1f","type":"discovered-from","created_at":"2026-01-31T00:31:22.974637948Z","created_by":"MagentaCompass"}]}
+{"id":"bd-33eoe","title":"[Bug] WebSocketHub handleReconnect can double-send ack-required messages","description":"In `apps/gateway/src/ws/hub.ts`, `handleReconnect()` replays missed messages for a channel and adds them to `pendingAcks`, then calls `replayPendingAcks()` which re-sends those newly-added pending messages a second time.\n\nThis can cause duplicate delivery on reconnect for ack-required channels.\n\nFix: ensure `replayPendingAcks()` only replays acks that existed prior to reconnect (or otherwise de-dupe against messages already replayed in this reconnect pass). Add regression test in `apps/gateway/src/ws/__tests__/ack-mode.test.ts`.","notes":"Blocked: NavyFinch currently holds exclusive reservations on hub.ts and ack-mode test; waiting for handoff or upstream fix.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"bug","assignee":"MagentaCompass","created_at":"2026-01-31T00:31:22.968156231Z","created_by":"MagentaCompass","updated_at":"2026-01-31T00:34:51.769227538Z","closed_at":"2026-01-31T00:34:51.769163999Z","close_reason":"Duplicate of bd-3qboo (fixed + pushed)","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-33eoe","depends_on_id":"bd-1ns1f","type":"discovered-from","created_at":"2026-01-31T00:31:22.974637948Z","created_by":"MagentaCompass"}]}
